1
00:01:54,479 --> 00:01:55,350
Your Majesty,

2
00:01:55,870 --> 00:01:56,680
you

3
00:01:57,120 --> 00:01:58,640
summoned me?

4
00:02:10,190 --> 00:02:11,030
Brother,

5
00:02:12,080 --> 00:02:13,340
what's wrong with you?

6
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,430
I

7
00:02:16,120 --> 00:02:17,910
have been sitting here for too long.

8
00:02:17,910 --> 00:02:19,310
My legs are a little numb.

9
00:02:19,840 --> 00:02:21,680
No matter how busy
you are with state affairs,

10
00:02:21,680 --> 00:02:23,880
you still need to get up and move around.

11
00:02:25,190 --> 00:02:26,280
Let me help you up.

12
00:02:26,470 --> 00:02:27,280
Take a few steps.

13
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:27,870
No need. Come.

14
00:02:27,870 --> 00:02:28,470
No need.

15
00:02:28,470 --> 00:02:29,600
Slow down, brother.

16
00:02:30,280 --> 00:02:31,360
Slow down.

17
00:02:32,430 --> 00:02:33,430
Be careful.

18
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:37,240
Brother.

19
00:02:37,470 --> 00:02:38,240
What is it?

20
00:02:38,560 --> 00:02:40,280
When you fell from the rooftop that night,

21
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,880
you didn’t get hurt, did you?

22
00:02:42,750 --> 00:02:44,590
Fell from the rooftop?

23
00:02:45,030 --> 00:02:46,829
How could that possibly hurt me?

24
00:02:46,870 --> 00:02:47,430
That's good.

25
00:02:47,430 --> 00:02:49,490
Don’t you remember when we were kids?

26
00:02:49,590 --> 00:02:50,400
Every day

27
00:02:51,150 --> 00:02:52,480
we were climbing trees,

28
00:02:52,630 --> 00:02:53,690
jumping off roofs,

29
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,360
and running all over the place—

30
00:02:55,360 --> 00:02:56,680
when did I get hurt?

31
00:02:57,430 --> 00:02:58,280
Ridiculous.

32
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,590
Then your waist...

33
00:03:00,360 --> 00:03:01,080
I forgot.

34
00:03:01,150 --> 00:03:02,950
It's numb from sitting too long.

35
00:03:03,280 --> 00:03:03,590
Right.

36
00:03:03,590 --> 00:03:04,590
Numb from sitting too long.

37
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:06,050
That time was an accident.

38
00:03:06,590 --> 00:03:08,590
You must not tell our eldest sister.

39
00:03:09,520 --> 00:03:10,320
I understand.

40
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:12,590
An accident.

41
00:03:13,310 --> 00:03:14,400
Whatever you say,

42
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:15,240
goes.

43
00:03:15,960 --> 00:03:17,560
You don't believe me, do you?

44
00:03:18,190 --> 00:03:19,430
If you don't believe me, let's go again.

45
00:03:19,430 --> 00:03:20,840
I'll definitely land on my feet.

46
00:03:20,840 --> 00:03:21,750
Brother,

47
00:03:22,240 --> 00:03:23,960
it's still bright outside.

48
00:03:24,310 --> 00:03:25,120
How about

49
00:03:25,520 --> 00:03:26,120
tonight?

50
00:03:28,710 --> 00:03:30,190
I can't go

51
00:03:30,190 --> 00:03:31,560
tonight.

52
00:03:32,000 --> 00:03:34,460
My eldest sister
is coming to see me tonight.

53
00:03:35,150 --> 00:03:36,430
The Eldest Princess?

54
00:03:36,430 --> 00:03:38,190
Then there's nothing I can do.

55
00:03:38,190 --> 00:03:39,120
I almost forgot.

56
00:03:39,400 --> 00:03:40,800
Xiao Chi and I arranged to drink

57
00:03:40,800 --> 00:03:42,079
in our bamboo forest.

58
00:03:42,750 --> 00:03:44,150
Then I will take my leave.

59
00:03:44,750 --> 00:03:46,150
You two brats

60
00:03:46,840 --> 00:03:48,400
are going drinking without me?

61
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:49,910
Do you mean

62
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:51,440
you can go with us, brother?

63
00:03:52,000 --> 00:03:54,360
Didn't I just say I can't go tonight?

64
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:56,560
My eldest sister is coming to see me.

65
00:03:56,960 --> 00:03:58,190
That's a pity.

66
00:03:58,560 --> 00:04:00,360
Since you can't join us, brother,

67
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,490
we'll just have to drink by ourselves.

68
00:04:02,560 --> 00:04:03,190
Wait.

69
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:05,030
I'll take my leave.

70
00:04:05,030 --> 00:04:05,710
Wait.

71
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:07,630
What a pity.

72
00:04:07,630 --> 00:04:08,470
Wait a minute.

73
00:04:09,590 --> 00:04:10,430
How about you

74
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,710
drinking here?

75
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:22,100
All I do every day is eat and sleep.

76
00:04:22,430 --> 00:04:24,310
I miss the sand seas of Changmo.

77
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,630
How about

78
00:04:25,870 --> 00:04:27,040
we go out for a walk?

79
00:04:27,430 --> 00:04:29,240
Will General Xiao agree to that?

80
00:04:29,240 --> 00:04:31,100
I heard Xiao Chi isn't here today.

81
00:04:31,360 --> 00:04:32,600
Let's sneak out.

82
00:04:33,600 --> 00:04:34,400
Let's go then.

83
00:04:51,560 --> 00:04:52,310
Jin Xi,

84
00:04:52,630 --> 00:04:53,159
let's go.

85
00:05:01,600 --> 00:05:02,390
Princess,

86
00:05:04,630 --> 00:05:05,760
where are you going?

87
00:05:06,750 --> 00:05:08,160
We are just looking around.

88
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:09,090
Looking around?

89
00:05:09,120 --> 00:05:09,720
I think

90
00:05:09,950 --> 00:05:11,510
you are about to leave, Princess.

91
00:05:11,510 --> 00:05:13,000
It's lunchtime.

92
00:05:13,190 --> 00:05:15,630
I brought you lunch myself.

93
00:05:15,750 --> 00:05:17,280
Please go back to your room.

94
00:05:17,560 --> 00:05:18,560
Don't run around.

95
00:05:19,600 --> 00:05:21,720
So we are not here
for a political marriage—

96
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:23,600
we came to the General's Mansion
to sit in prison.

97
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,120
No.

98
00:05:24,430 --> 00:05:25,600
She makes sense.

99
00:05:27,430 --> 00:05:28,290
Physician Han,

100
00:05:30,830 --> 00:05:32,800
General Xiao is busy outside every day.

101
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,950
It's one thing that he can't stay in
the manor with the princess,

102
00:05:34,950 --> 00:05:37,510
but she can't even go out for a walk?

103
00:05:38,240 --> 00:05:39,120
No.

104
00:05:39,270 --> 00:05:41,240
I'm just afraid

105
00:05:41,240 --> 00:05:42,360
it's not safe on the streets.

106
00:05:42,360 --> 00:05:43,800
What could be unsafe?

107
00:05:44,120 --> 00:05:45,390
Being cooped up in the room every day

108
00:05:45,390 --> 00:05:46,790
will drive anyone crazy.

109
00:05:47,480 --> 00:05:48,240
As it happens,

110
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,510
I'm going out today.

111
00:05:50,120 --> 00:05:51,560
The princess can be with me.

112
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:52,270
Yeah.

113
00:05:52,630 --> 00:05:53,510
With Physician Han here,

114
00:05:53,510 --> 00:05:54,600
you don't have to worry.

115
00:05:54,600 --> 00:05:55,040
Let's go.

116
00:05:55,040 --> 00:05:55,750
Wait.

117
00:05:56,430 --> 00:05:58,159
Don't worry, Vice General Xu,

118
00:05:58,310 --> 00:06:00,190
we will come back safely.

119
00:06:00,600 --> 00:06:01,870
Don't worry?

120
00:06:03,830 --> 00:06:05,390
We don’t have streets
this lively and bustling

121
00:06:05,390 --> 00:06:07,040
back in Changmo.

122
00:06:07,870 --> 00:06:10,270
So you should come out
and walk around more.

123
00:06:10,430 --> 00:06:12,630
Crowds inevitably lead to trouble.

124
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,480
Physician Han,

125
00:06:14,480 --> 00:06:15,310
the sachet.

126
00:06:20,560 --> 00:06:21,190
Bro.

127
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:21,870
Look at

128
00:06:22,040 --> 00:06:23,240
that girl over there.

129
00:06:24,720 --> 00:06:26,310
What a small world.

130
00:06:26,830 --> 00:06:28,390
The one next to her looks pretty good too.

131
00:06:28,390 --> 00:06:28,800
Bro,

132
00:06:28,800 --> 00:06:31,310
let's not mess with that girl for now.

133
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,750
Yeah, Bro, I'm scared.

134
00:06:33,510 --> 00:06:34,560
You coward.

135
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,390
I don't believe

136
00:06:35,390 --> 00:06:37,630
anyone will come to help them today.

137
00:06:38,120 --> 00:06:38,560
Boss,

138
00:06:38,560 --> 00:06:39,190
I want two.

139
00:06:39,870 --> 00:06:40,630
Okay, miss.

140
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:49,950
Jin Xi!

141
00:06:51,800 --> 00:06:52,750
There are pinwheels here.

142
00:06:52,750 --> 00:06:53,270
Miss,

143
00:06:53,270 --> 00:06:54,070
pick one.

144
00:06:54,510 --> 00:06:55,040
Let's go.

145
00:06:56,950 --> 00:06:58,240
Which one do you like?

146
00:06:59,120 --> 00:07:00,180
Let me see this one.

147
00:07:04,120 --> 00:07:05,180
What are you doing?

148
00:07:05,240 --> 00:07:06,800
These two girls

149
00:07:06,920 --> 00:07:07,950
are pretty nice, aren’t they?

150
00:07:07,950 --> 00:07:09,560
None of your business.

151
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,800
What do you think

152
00:07:12,070 --> 00:07:13,720
of me?

153
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:18,050
One offered herself up?

154
00:07:18,750 --> 00:07:19,920
Oh, very nice.

155
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:20,450
Let's go.

156
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,870
This girl is great.

157
00:07:22,270 --> 00:07:22,430
Go.

158
00:07:22,430 --> 00:07:23,600
Hurry up.

159
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:28,360
Keep up.

160
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,630
Hurry up.

161
00:07:30,390 --> 00:07:31,040
Coming.

162
00:07:32,310 --> 00:07:33,190
Second Brother,

163
00:07:33,190 --> 00:07:34,190
where is this?

164
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:36,250
You don't remember?

165
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,860
I don't remember much.

166
00:07:39,190 --> 00:07:40,800
This is the bamboo forest

167
00:07:40,800 --> 00:07:42,360
you, Oldest Brother, and I planted

168
00:07:42,360 --> 00:07:44,240
before you went to Tianlang Pass.

169
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:46,560
At that time, this bamboo forest

170
00:07:46,560 --> 00:07:48,000
wasn't even as tall as me.

171
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:50,040
So how many years have you been gone?

172
00:07:50,040 --> 00:07:50,800
Come here.

173
00:07:53,430 --> 00:07:55,830
Since we're revisiting
our old haunt today,

174
00:07:55,830 --> 00:07:57,890
we must drink to our heart's content.

175
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:03,000
Let me pour a drink for General Xiao.

176
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,270
Then

177
00:08:04,270 --> 00:08:05,830
thank you, Lord Fei.

178
00:08:08,830 --> 00:08:10,490
But without big brother here,

179
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:12,600
it feels a bit less exciting.

180
00:08:14,190 --> 00:08:15,950
Since His Majesty ascended the throne,

181
00:08:15,950 --> 00:08:18,880
he really has few opportunities
to leave the palace.

182
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,900
How about this?

183
00:08:20,630 --> 00:08:21,360
In the future,

184
00:08:21,360 --> 00:08:22,690
we two will find a chance

185
00:08:22,920 --> 00:08:24,630
to secretly bring him here.

186
00:08:26,920 --> 00:08:27,360
Then

187
00:08:27,600 --> 00:08:28,720
let's toast to big brother.

188
00:08:28,720 --> 00:08:29,580
To big brother.

189
00:08:36,240 --> 00:08:39,770
Miss, come take a look at
these styles and see which one you like.

190
00:08:39,789 --> 00:08:40,720
Princess,

191
00:08:40,720 --> 00:08:42,380
these earrings suit you well.

192
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,030
Very beautiful.

193
00:08:44,150 --> 00:08:45,150
Boss, wrap it up.

194
00:08:45,630 --> 00:08:47,160
You have great taste, miss.

195
00:08:47,720 --> 00:08:48,600
Physician Han,

196
00:08:48,960 --> 00:08:50,840
we traveled all the way
from Tianlang Pass,

197
00:08:50,840 --> 00:08:52,240
and you cured my illness.

198
00:08:52,550 --> 00:08:54,030
Let's not be strangers from now on.

199
00:08:54,030 --> 00:08:55,150
Call me Wanyu.

200
00:08:55,630 --> 00:08:57,960
Then I won't stand on ceremony, Princess.

201
00:08:58,320 --> 00:08:59,120
Wanyu.

202
00:08:59,750 --> 00:09:00,390
Yunling.

203
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:12,800
This suits Jin Xi perfectly.

204
00:09:16,360 --> 00:09:17,510
Where is Jin Xi?

205
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,260
I've been here the whole time.

206
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,440
Jin Xi, turn around.

207
00:09:28,360 --> 00:09:29,750
Hurry up.

208
00:09:43,550 --> 00:09:44,750
You have great taste.

209
00:09:45,200 --> 00:09:46,840
We picked it together.

210
00:09:50,150 --> 00:09:50,680
Hurry up.

211
00:09:50,750 --> 00:09:52,030
There's more fun stuff ahead.

212
00:09:52,030 --> 00:09:52,560
Let's go.

213
00:09:53,200 --> 00:09:54,120
Excuse me.

214
00:09:55,240 --> 00:09:56,030
Thank you.

215
00:09:57,320 --> 00:09:58,150
Let's go.

216
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,990
You’ve finally made it back,

217
00:10:11,080 --> 00:10:12,390
so don’t leave again.

218
00:10:18,910 --> 00:10:20,390
I’m used to life in the military camp.

219
00:10:20,390 --> 00:10:22,390
If I suddenly had to stay in the capital,

220
00:10:22,390 --> 00:10:24,320
I'm afraid I wouldn't be used to it.

221
00:10:26,510 --> 00:10:27,600
What if

222
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:31,100
Physician Han also stayed in
the capital and didn't leave?

223
00:10:33,630 --> 00:10:34,750
She...

224
00:10:37,320 --> 00:10:39,200
She will probably take her brother

225
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,200
back to Changmo.

226
00:10:40,630 --> 00:10:42,200
It's easy to make her stay.

227
00:10:45,320 --> 00:10:46,790
Just settle her down

228
00:10:47,240 --> 00:10:48,370
here in the capital.

229
00:10:50,150 --> 00:10:51,080
Second Brother,

230
00:10:52,030 --> 00:10:53,560
what are you talking about?

231
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,330
I don't understand.

232
00:10:55,630 --> 00:10:56,890
You don't understand?

233
00:11:00,080 --> 00:11:01,440
Forget it then.

234
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,870
As the Minister of Revenue, I have

235
00:11:05,320 --> 00:11:08,240
countless houses and fertile lands
under my control.

236
00:11:08,240 --> 00:11:09,100
How about this.

237
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,270
After I go back,

238
00:11:10,360 --> 00:11:11,630
I will pick one

239
00:11:11,840 --> 00:11:13,570
and give it to her. Will that do?

240
00:11:17,150 --> 00:11:18,120
She

241
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,840
is not the kind of person to seek comfort.

242
00:11:21,840 --> 00:11:23,120
This won't work,

243
00:11:23,120 --> 00:11:24,250
and that won't work.

244
00:11:25,390 --> 00:11:26,240
Tell me,

245
00:11:27,030 --> 00:11:27,960
what should I do?

246
00:11:30,150 --> 00:11:31,320
How would I know

247
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,200
what she's thinking?

248
00:11:36,550 --> 00:11:37,680
Judging by the time,

249
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:39,240
you should go back

250
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:40,600
and let her treat you.

251
00:11:45,960 --> 00:11:47,200
Go back.

252
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,030
You brat,

253
00:11:52,390 --> 00:11:55,120
do you think I don't know
what you're thinking?

254
00:11:57,600 --> 00:11:59,200
I brought you your medicine.

255
00:12:01,840 --> 00:12:03,300
You took the Princess out?

256
00:12:03,550 --> 00:12:06,150
She's been locked up
ever since she arrived in the capital.

257
00:12:06,150 --> 00:12:07,200
If you keep locking her up,

258
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:08,200
she will go crazy.

259
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,550
If anything happens to her,

260
00:12:09,550 --> 00:12:11,480
who will take the responsibility?

261
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:16,360
I didn't think it through.

262
00:12:16,440 --> 00:12:17,700
It won't happen again.

263
00:12:21,120 --> 00:12:22,440
This is my duty.

264
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:23,980
I hope you understand.

265
00:12:25,030 --> 00:12:25,840
Yeah.

266
00:12:32,360 --> 00:12:34,120
This mandarin duck embroidery
is quite nice.

267
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:34,870
Right?

268
00:12:34,870 --> 00:12:36,030
It is quite nice.

269
00:12:36,440 --> 00:12:38,320
But as a young woman in Jinglan,

270
00:12:38,320 --> 00:12:39,630
aren’t you afraid people will gossip

271
00:12:39,630 --> 00:12:40,750
if you go around so openly

272
00:12:40,750 --> 00:12:42,350
with a mandarin duck sachet?

273
00:12:44,150 --> 00:12:47,080
Then I will just say
it was given to me by General Xiao.

274
00:12:50,790 --> 00:12:53,200
Well then,
since it’s reciprocity between courtesy,

275
00:12:53,200 --> 00:12:55,600
what should you give me in return?

276
00:12:57,240 --> 00:13:00,040
It's a waste of your talent
not to be a businessman.

277
00:13:01,390 --> 00:13:02,510
It's just a sachet.

278
00:13:02,600 --> 00:13:04,320
I'll give General Xiao one in return.

279
00:13:04,320 --> 00:13:05,790
But rest assured, General.

280
00:13:05,790 --> 00:13:08,480
Mine doesn't have lovebirds on it.

281
00:13:09,200 --> 00:13:10,630
I put a lot of herbs in it.

282
00:13:10,870 --> 00:13:12,750
It's great for preventing diseases.

283
00:13:12,750 --> 00:13:13,910
Please, General,

284
00:13:13,910 --> 00:13:15,550
make sure to keep it with you.

285
00:13:33,360 --> 00:13:34,120
My Lord,

286
00:13:34,320 --> 00:13:36,000
Xiao Chi wants to see you.

287
00:13:38,440 --> 00:13:41,320
So he actually thought of coming here.

288
00:13:43,750 --> 00:13:45,030
Let him in.

289
00:13:45,150 --> 00:13:45,720
Yes.

290
00:13:50,440 --> 00:13:51,320
Lord Zhang.

291
00:13:51,910 --> 00:13:53,080
General Xiao.

292
00:13:54,120 --> 00:13:55,390
What brings you

293
00:13:55,390 --> 00:13:57,320
here?

294
00:13:57,750 --> 00:14:00,240
Lord Zhang is the chief minister
of the court.

295
00:14:00,240 --> 00:14:01,750
Having returned from Tianlang Pass,

296
00:14:01,750 --> 00:14:03,600
naturally I came to pay my respects.

297
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:04,630
In that case,

298
00:14:04,630 --> 00:14:06,720
if I don't invite you to sit,

299
00:14:06,790 --> 00:14:09,390
it would make me seem unreasonable.

300
00:14:09,390 --> 00:14:10,520
Please, have a seat.

301
00:14:16,320 --> 00:14:17,030
Come,

302
00:14:17,030 --> 00:14:18,200
General Xiao.

303
00:14:21,840 --> 00:14:22,910
General Xiao,

304
00:14:23,360 --> 00:14:24,720
you've come at a bad time.

305
00:14:24,720 --> 00:14:26,320
We're out of tea in the manor.

306
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,670
No matter.

307
00:14:28,030 --> 00:14:28,960
I didn't come

308
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:30,750
for tea today.

309
00:14:31,240 --> 00:14:32,370
I just didn't expect

310
00:14:32,480 --> 00:14:34,000
that Lord Zhang's massive manor

311
00:14:34,000 --> 00:14:35,240
would be out of water.

312
00:14:35,320 --> 00:14:36,550
How incorruptible.

313
00:14:36,550 --> 00:14:37,870
As an official,

314
00:14:37,870 --> 00:14:40,070
I serve the Emperor and the court above,

315
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,960
and the common people below.

316
00:14:42,150 --> 00:14:44,440
As a childless widower,

317
00:14:45,000 --> 00:14:46,910
why would I need so much money?

318
00:14:46,910 --> 00:14:48,030
General Xiao,

319
00:14:48,030 --> 00:14:49,630
just say what you want to say.

320
00:14:49,630 --> 00:14:51,390
Don't delay me

321
00:14:51,840 --> 00:14:52,960
from my reading.

322
00:14:53,910 --> 00:14:55,240
Lord Zhang is straightforward.

323
00:14:55,240 --> 00:14:57,200
Then I'll get straight to the point.

324
00:14:57,200 --> 00:15:00,030
I wonder if Lord Zhang knows anything

325
00:15:01,000 --> 00:15:01,840
about the death of Judge Xue.

326
00:15:01,840 --> 00:15:02,960
Judge Xue?

327
00:15:05,000 --> 00:15:07,200
Judge Xue.

328
00:15:07,390 --> 00:15:09,630
Which Judge Xue are you talking about?

329
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,080
The Judge Xue who

330
00:15:11,270 --> 00:15:13,790
presided over the Han family massacre.

331
00:15:14,550 --> 00:15:15,440
Oh,

332
00:15:17,030 --> 00:15:18,840
I think I remember.

333
00:15:20,360 --> 00:15:21,390
He's dead?

334
00:15:23,720 --> 00:15:25,390
But it's not surprising.

335
00:15:25,790 --> 00:15:27,550
We are all getting old.

336
00:15:27,750 --> 00:15:29,240
Birth, old age, sickness, and death

337
00:15:29,240 --> 00:15:31,720
are up to heaven, not ourselves.

338
00:15:31,720 --> 00:15:32,720
Lord Zhang,

339
00:15:34,320 --> 00:15:35,960
he was murdered.

340
00:15:37,960 --> 00:15:39,670
Murdered?

341
00:15:40,320 --> 00:15:42,670
Then you should hurry up and find

342
00:15:42,670 --> 00:15:44,440
the constables investigating the case.

343
00:15:44,440 --> 00:15:46,240
Why did you come to me?

344
00:15:46,600 --> 00:15:47,360
Do you

345
00:15:47,790 --> 00:15:49,150
suspect me?

346
00:15:49,630 --> 00:15:52,000
Then you have to produce evidence.

347
00:15:52,440 --> 00:15:53,910
How could I suspect

348
00:15:53,910 --> 00:15:55,640
the incorruptible Lord Zhang?

349
00:15:59,480 --> 00:16:00,360
General Xiao,

350
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:01,790
what made you

351
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:04,440
think of looking for Judge Xue?

352
00:16:05,670 --> 00:16:07,120
I wanted to ask about

353
00:16:07,120 --> 00:16:09,440
the details of the Han family massacre.

354
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:14,840
That was many years ago.

355
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:16,870
Does Lord Zhang

356
00:16:16,870 --> 00:16:18,630
know what happened back then?

357
00:16:19,840 --> 00:16:21,360
Many years ago,

358
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:23,840
the entire population of Jinglan

359
00:16:24,150 --> 00:16:26,150
was suffering from a severe plague.

360
00:16:26,630 --> 00:16:28,000
Every household hung white banners.

361
00:16:28,000 --> 00:16:29,660
There were dead in every home.

362
00:16:29,790 --> 00:16:32,000
It was truly unbearable to see.

363
00:16:32,150 --> 00:16:34,000
As for the Han family,

364
00:16:34,000 --> 00:16:35,910
I know a little.

365
00:16:35,960 --> 00:16:37,910
It’s said they administered
the wrong medicine,

366
00:16:37,910 --> 00:16:39,000
which led to patient deaths,

367
00:16:39,000 --> 00:16:41,860
and that’s why they were executed
as a whole family.

368
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:44,150
If anyone from the Han family

369
00:16:44,630 --> 00:16:46,150
managed to escape

370
00:16:46,150 --> 00:16:47,840
that massacre back then,

371
00:16:47,840 --> 00:16:50,440
they should reflect deeply on themselves.

372
00:16:50,630 --> 00:16:53,030
See if it was heaven's mercy

373
00:16:53,030 --> 00:16:55,240
or if they got what they deserved.

374
00:17:01,120 --> 00:17:02,120
General Xiao,

375
00:17:03,630 --> 00:17:04,720
if

376
00:17:04,720 --> 00:17:06,200
there is nothing else,

377
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:09,349
I would like to rest.

378
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:11,510
Alright.

379
00:17:13,200 --> 00:17:14,069
In that case,

380
00:17:14,790 --> 00:17:16,990
I will not bother Lord Zhang any longer.

381
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,510
Take care, General Xiao.

382
00:17:25,640 --> 00:17:27,790
This Xiao Chi.

383
00:17:35,110 --> 00:17:35,960
Princess.

384
00:17:36,400 --> 00:17:37,510
Jin Xi,

385
00:17:37,510 --> 00:17:38,400
where did you go?

386
00:17:38,400 --> 00:17:39,550
Why are you so late?

387
00:17:40,400 --> 00:17:42,640
I thought the night was lovely,

388
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,240
so we could have a drink.

389
00:17:44,830 --> 00:17:45,640
Yes.

390
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,310
Today

391
00:17:47,310 --> 00:17:49,550
is Changmo's annual Sand Festival.

392
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,860
In previous years,
I always spent it with my father.

393
00:17:53,310 --> 00:17:54,160
This year...

394
00:17:54,160 --> 00:17:55,000
Right.

395
00:17:55,400 --> 00:17:57,110
Today is the annual
Sand Sacrifice Festival.

396
00:17:57,110 --> 00:17:58,440
We should drink

397
00:17:58,440 --> 00:17:59,110
and dance.

398
00:18:01,200 --> 00:18:02,400
We have wine.

399
00:18:02,440 --> 00:18:03,160
How about this?

400
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:04,240
You have a drink first.

401
00:18:04,240 --> 00:18:06,310
I'll go invite Physician Han over,

402
00:18:06,550 --> 00:18:08,280
and we can celebrate together.

403
00:18:08,590 --> 00:18:09,590
That sounds good.

404
00:18:15,750 --> 00:18:16,550
Well,

405
00:18:19,270 --> 00:18:20,400
you practice first.

406
00:18:20,510 --> 00:18:22,270
I'll go get Physician Han now.

407
00:18:22,590 --> 00:18:23,480
Okay.

408
00:19:15,720 --> 00:19:16,520
What's wrong?

409
00:19:17,590 --> 00:19:18,720
Why did you stop dancing?

410
00:19:18,720 --> 00:19:19,310
I...

411
00:19:19,920 --> 00:19:21,830
I didn't expect anyone to come.

412
00:19:23,110 --> 00:19:24,920
You danced beautifully just now, Princess.

413
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,590
I...

414
00:19:28,720 --> 00:19:30,980
It really makes me want to keep watching.

415
00:19:33,640 --> 00:19:35,350
Where did Jin Xi go?

416
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:38,100
Who are you talking about?

417
00:19:38,110 --> 00:19:38,790
No one.

418
00:19:39,510 --> 00:19:41,590
I meant you were in a hurry last time,

419
00:19:41,590 --> 00:19:43,920
and said you'd tell me
your name this time.

420
00:19:43,920 --> 00:19:45,450
Why haven't you told me yet?

421
00:19:49,310 --> 00:19:50,440
I...

422
00:19:52,640 --> 00:19:54,720
If I tell her I am Liu Chu,

423
00:19:54,920 --> 00:19:56,250
that would be so boring.

424
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:59,640
But who can I be right now?

425
00:20:01,000 --> 00:20:02,310
Didn't I say last time?

426
00:20:02,350 --> 00:20:04,030
My relationship with Xiao Chi

427
00:20:04,030 --> 00:20:05,920
is as close as brothers.

428
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:08,240
Just now, seeing you dance so beautifully—

429
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:09,550
it was like a fairy

430
00:20:09,960 --> 00:20:11,160
descending to earth.

431
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:12,640
May I invite you

432
00:20:13,310 --> 00:20:14,030
for a drink?

433
00:20:17,790 --> 00:20:19,550
Why hasn't Jin Xi returned yet?

434
00:20:21,790 --> 00:20:23,520
Then I'll have a drink with you.

435
00:20:27,960 --> 00:20:29,200
I wonder

436
00:20:29,720 --> 00:20:31,830
how things will go for them tonight.

437
00:20:33,960 --> 00:20:35,590
No matter how it goes,

438
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:37,790
it's good for them to interact more.

439
00:20:38,240 --> 00:20:39,550
If their bond grows,

440
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:42,590
the peace between our countries will last.

441
00:20:42,590 --> 00:20:43,830
How troublesome.

442
00:20:44,400 --> 00:20:45,030
In this world,

443
00:20:45,030 --> 00:20:47,230
there are far more troublesome things.

444
00:20:47,830 --> 00:20:48,590
Sometimes,

445
00:20:48,920 --> 00:20:51,450
I really just want to kill Liu Chu
with my sword

446
00:20:52,000 --> 00:20:54,000
and take his head back
to report my mission.

447
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,240
You can't kill Liu Chu.

448
00:20:55,240 --> 00:20:56,720
Remember your mission

449
00:20:56,880 --> 00:20:58,070
is to protect the Princess

450
00:20:58,070 --> 00:21:00,270
and facilitate the marriage alliance.

451
00:21:00,590 --> 00:21:02,200
Even if Liu Chu deserves to die,

452
00:21:02,200 --> 00:21:03,590
how and when he dies

453
00:21:03,750 --> 00:21:05,210
is the King Mo's business.

454
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:07,160
Don't take any risks.

455
00:21:11,510 --> 00:21:13,510
Liu Chu and Xiao Chi are my brothers.

456
00:21:14,510 --> 00:21:15,590
If one day

457
00:21:16,200 --> 00:21:18,000
they really must die,

458
00:21:18,640 --> 00:21:19,590
I hope

459
00:21:21,590 --> 00:21:23,350
I'm the one to kill them.

460
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:25,830
You seem

461
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,590
different from before.

462
00:21:28,240 --> 00:21:29,640
You're overthinking it.

463
00:21:29,920 --> 00:21:31,050
I've never changed.

464
00:21:34,400 --> 00:21:35,790
So you've

465
00:21:36,030 --> 00:21:37,960
lived in Changmo since you were little.

466
00:21:37,960 --> 00:21:38,750
Yeah.

467
00:21:39,590 --> 00:21:40,750
Ever since I can remember,

468
00:21:40,750 --> 00:21:42,640
I grew up by my father's side.

469
00:21:43,030 --> 00:21:44,440
Other than my father,

470
00:21:44,960 --> 00:21:46,830
I rarely saw other men.

471
00:21:49,960 --> 00:21:51,350
Changmo?

472
00:21:51,750 --> 00:21:53,200
What kind of place is it?

473
00:21:53,590 --> 00:21:55,110
Our Changmo,

474
00:21:55,310 --> 00:21:56,790
is a wonderful place.

475
00:21:57,440 --> 00:21:58,960
The vast yellow sands

476
00:21:59,030 --> 00:22:00,480
stretch endlessly.

477
00:22:00,790 --> 00:22:03,270
That little oasis in the yellow sand

478
00:22:03,400 --> 00:22:04,830
is just like

479
00:22:05,830 --> 00:22:08,030
as bright as the stars.

480
00:22:09,640 --> 00:22:11,240
Since it's such a nice place,

481
00:22:11,400 --> 00:22:13,260
there must be a lot of good things.

482
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:14,830
Mm-hmm.

483
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,330
Although the yellow sand is magnificent,

484
00:22:18,550 --> 00:22:19,960
our resources

485
00:22:19,960 --> 00:22:22,270
are indeed not as abundant as Jinglan's.

486
00:22:24,750 --> 00:22:26,160
If...

487
00:22:26,830 --> 00:22:28,440
If I were Liu Chu,

488
00:22:28,590 --> 00:22:29,920
I would definitely hope

489
00:22:30,110 --> 00:22:31,350
our two countries could be on good terms

490
00:22:31,350 --> 00:22:32,590
and open trade routes.

491
00:22:32,590 --> 00:22:35,390
We could send good things
from Jinglan to Changmo,

492
00:22:35,590 --> 00:22:38,310
and let the people of Changmo
come here to do business.

493
00:22:38,310 --> 00:22:42,040
This way, the relationship
between our countries would be closer,

494
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,510
and life would be more prosperous.

495
00:22:46,590 --> 00:22:47,680
And if

496
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:50,160
anyone dares to invade Changmo,

497
00:22:50,480 --> 00:22:52,590
I will definitely lead troops into battle

498
00:22:52,590 --> 00:22:54,250
and wipe them out completely.

499
00:22:59,000 --> 00:22:59,880
Why

500
00:23:00,440 --> 00:23:01,440
are you laughing?

501
00:23:02,830 --> 00:23:03,830
Nothing.

502
00:23:08,110 --> 00:23:09,240
You

503
00:23:09,550 --> 00:23:11,480
are here for a political marriage?

504
00:23:11,510 --> 00:23:13,440
You haven't even seen
what Liu Chu looks like.

505
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:15,160
Why do you want to marry him?

506
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:18,030
What if he's an old man,

507
00:23:18,030 --> 00:23:18,880
or

508
00:23:19,200 --> 00:23:20,440
ugly?

509
00:23:20,790 --> 00:23:21,720
He won't be.

510
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:23,680
My father told me

511
00:23:24,110 --> 00:23:26,310
Liu Chu is only a few years older than me.

512
00:23:26,510 --> 00:23:27,550
Besides,

513
00:23:29,440 --> 00:23:31,350
I've seen his portrait.

514
00:23:34,000 --> 00:23:35,640
You've seen his portrait?

515
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:41,310
Then how do you think

516
00:23:41,640 --> 00:23:44,510
he compares

517
00:23:45,920 --> 00:23:46,750
to me?

518
00:23:48,160 --> 00:23:50,440
You are a handsome man,

519
00:23:51,440 --> 00:23:53,160
but in my heart,

520
00:23:53,720 --> 00:23:55,200
there is only Liu Chu.

521
00:23:57,400 --> 00:23:59,330
What exactly do you love about him?

522
00:23:59,440 --> 00:24:01,240
My father says he is

523
00:24:01,960 --> 00:24:03,550
wise and mighty,

524
00:24:03,720 --> 00:24:04,830
magnanimous,

525
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,790
a blessing to the people,

526
00:24:06,960 --> 00:24:09,490
and loves his subjects
like his own children.

527
00:24:10,110 --> 00:24:11,110
Besides,

528
00:24:11,440 --> 00:24:13,310
on my way to the capital,

529
00:24:13,510 --> 00:24:15,240
I saw the people living in peace

530
00:24:15,510 --> 00:24:16,970
and the streets bustling.

531
00:24:17,240 --> 00:24:19,000
It proves my father didn't lie to me.

532
00:24:19,000 --> 00:24:20,590
Liu Chu is a good king.

533
00:24:21,510 --> 00:24:22,350
I...

534
00:24:25,720 --> 00:24:26,550
He...

535
00:24:27,160 --> 00:24:29,510
He can't be that good, right?

536
00:24:29,750 --> 00:24:30,720
Come, let me toast you again.

537
00:24:30,720 --> 00:24:31,050
Come.

538
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,310
Then

539
00:24:38,960 --> 00:24:40,880
how can you be sure

540
00:24:41,440 --> 00:24:43,840
that he will love you
as much as you love him?

541
00:24:44,920 --> 00:24:46,400
My father told me

542
00:24:46,640 --> 00:24:48,240
we are a match made in heaven,

543
00:24:48,640 --> 00:24:50,400
destined by fate.

544
00:24:50,750 --> 00:24:52,950
He will definitely fall in love with me.

545
00:24:55,510 --> 00:24:57,200
That makes some sense.

546
00:24:57,830 --> 00:24:58,590
In that case,

547
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:01,920
I wish you and Liu Chu

548
00:25:02,960 --> 00:25:04,920
a harmonious union
lasting a hundred years,

549
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,180
early birth of an heir,

550
00:25:06,200 --> 00:25:07,160
growing old together,

551
00:25:07,160 --> 00:25:08,760
and a century of mutual love.

552
00:25:09,030 --> 00:25:10,110
Then I wish you

553
00:25:10,640 --> 00:25:12,310
to find your beloved soon.

554
00:25:13,960 --> 00:25:17,000
Actually, I think I already have.

555
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:34,790
Princess,

556
00:25:35,070 --> 00:25:36,160
that dance earlier

557
00:25:36,640 --> 00:25:37,830
was beautiful.

558
00:25:38,830 --> 00:25:39,790
Could you

559
00:25:41,790 --> 00:25:42,590
dance again?

560
00:25:43,550 --> 00:25:45,200
I'll pass on the dancing.

561
00:25:45,350 --> 00:25:46,510
It's getting late today,

562
00:25:46,510 --> 00:25:48,590
and it's not appropriate
for us to drink here.

563
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:50,270
I'm going to find Jin Xi first.

564
00:26:33,480 --> 00:26:34,510
Why are you here?

565
00:26:38,550 --> 00:26:39,920
I wanted to take a walk,

566
00:26:40,440 --> 00:26:41,970
and somehow I ended up here.

567
00:26:43,920 --> 00:26:44,750
Did you

568
00:26:45,240 --> 00:26:46,750
remember something?

569
00:26:48,920 --> 00:26:51,160
Was I supposed to remember something?

570
00:26:53,750 --> 00:26:54,950
This river is so deep.

571
00:26:55,200 --> 00:26:56,400
If you fall in,

572
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:57,590
we'll both die.

573
00:27:01,510 --> 00:27:02,110
I

574
00:27:02,110 --> 00:27:03,160
didn't mean that.

575
00:27:07,790 --> 00:27:09,790
Thank you for helping me find my brother

576
00:27:09,790 --> 00:27:11,720
and for investigating Lord Zhang.

577
00:27:11,830 --> 00:27:12,720
It's nothing.

578
00:27:14,030 --> 00:27:15,110
Actually,

579
00:27:16,240 --> 00:27:18,160
things might not go that smoothly.

580
00:27:18,160 --> 00:27:20,160
If it really comes to a point
where the investigation can’t continue

581
00:27:20,160 --> 00:27:21,620
there's nothing we can do.

582
00:27:21,830 --> 00:27:23,160
But before that,

583
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:24,960
I won't give up.

584
00:27:28,920 --> 00:27:30,400
When I was young,

585
00:27:30,680 --> 00:27:31,880
I met a girl

586
00:27:32,030 --> 00:27:33,690
who said the same thing as you.

587
00:27:36,110 --> 00:27:38,000
Is the girl you mentioned

588
00:27:38,310 --> 00:27:39,440
me?

589
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:42,000
What if I said yes?

590
00:27:45,400 --> 00:27:46,550
I'm just kidding.

591
00:27:49,750 --> 00:27:50,830
I'm serious.

592
00:28:07,350 --> 00:28:08,160
Brother.

593
00:28:08,960 --> 00:28:10,090
You wanted to see me?

594
00:28:10,510 --> 00:28:11,110
Yes.

595
00:28:12,440 --> 00:28:13,240
Second Brother,

596
00:28:13,240 --> 00:28:15,240
has Xiao Chi received

597
00:28:15,240 --> 00:28:16,480
any news from

598
00:28:16,480 --> 00:28:17,880
Tianlang Pass recently?

599
00:28:17,920 --> 00:28:19,790
How would I know?

600
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:21,550
But since Third Brother
hasn't reported anything,

601
00:28:21,550 --> 00:28:23,350
it means the border is peaceful.

602
00:28:23,550 --> 00:28:24,280
Makes sense.

603
00:28:25,590 --> 00:28:29,350
It seems relations
between Jinglan and Changmo are improving,

604
00:28:29,350 --> 00:28:30,160
doesn’t it?”

605
00:28:30,830 --> 00:28:33,920
Now that the Princess has just
arrived in the capital,

606
00:28:34,200 --> 00:28:36,200
it has brought peace to the borders.

607
00:28:36,790 --> 00:28:38,400
When the marriage alliance is completed,

608
00:28:38,400 --> 00:28:39,750
Jinglan and Changmo

609
00:28:39,750 --> 00:28:41,550
will surely be at peace forever.

610
00:28:43,550 --> 00:28:45,750
You are temporarily
in charge of the Ministry of Rites.

611
00:28:45,750 --> 00:28:46,960
So when do you think

612
00:28:46,960 --> 00:28:48,590
the ceremony should be held?

613
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:50,720
Brother,

614
00:28:50,920 --> 00:28:52,830
I have long been prepared for this.

615
00:28:52,830 --> 00:28:54,510
I've been carrying this
until it's almost worn out.

616
00:28:54,510 --> 00:28:55,400
Come on.

617
00:28:55,400 --> 00:28:56,510
This is the Imperial Astronomical
Bureau’s auspicious dates

618
00:28:56,510 --> 00:28:58,750
for the next six months.

619
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,800
Please take a look, brother.

620
00:29:09,200 --> 00:29:12,270
I was thinking that good relations
between Jinglan and Changmo

621
00:29:12,270 --> 00:29:13,600
will benefit the people

622
00:29:13,750 --> 00:29:15,200
and ensure

623
00:29:15,200 --> 00:29:16,510
everlasting peace.

624
00:29:17,310 --> 00:29:18,350
Whatever Your Majesty does

625
00:29:18,350 --> 00:29:21,210
is definitely
for the sake of the people of Jinglan.

626
00:29:21,480 --> 00:29:22,160
Of course.

627
00:29:22,350 --> 00:29:23,000
Of course.

628
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:25,330
So which day do you think

629
00:29:25,440 --> 00:29:26,920
is the best?

630
00:29:27,440 --> 00:29:29,700
Brother, these are all auspicious days.

631
00:29:29,790 --> 00:29:31,550
But if you ask me,

632
00:29:31,550 --> 00:29:33,030
it should be as soon as possible,

633
00:29:33,030 --> 00:29:34,630
like the tenth of next month.

634
00:29:36,000 --> 00:29:37,000
So soon?

635
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:37,720
The Princess of Changmo

636
00:29:37,720 --> 00:29:39,550
has been in the capital for a while.

637
00:29:39,550 --> 00:29:41,160
If we delay any longer,

638
00:29:41,160 --> 00:29:43,240
I'm afraid Changmo will be suspicious.

639
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:46,920
But what about the many matters
regarding the marriage ceremony?

640
00:29:47,750 --> 00:29:49,240
Rest assured, Brother.

641
00:29:49,240 --> 00:29:50,830
Since returning to the capital,

642
00:29:50,830 --> 00:29:52,400
I've already started

643
00:29:52,400 --> 00:29:54,110
planning and arranging it.

644
00:29:56,240 --> 00:29:58,240
No wonder you’re my second brother.

645
00:29:58,720 --> 00:29:59,510
Good.

646
00:30:00,240 --> 00:30:01,400
Then,

647
00:30:01,960 --> 00:30:03,350
Brother, we...

648
00:30:10,240 --> 00:30:11,720
B-Brother.

649
00:30:12,480 --> 00:30:14,350
I'm done here.

650
00:30:15,350 --> 00:30:17,350
Go about your business.

651
00:30:19,550 --> 00:30:20,270
Then,

652
00:30:20,720 --> 00:30:22,320
Brother, I'll take my leave.

653
00:30:32,590 --> 00:30:33,920
So it seems

654
00:30:34,200 --> 00:30:35,720
Wanyue and Liu Chu

655
00:30:36,510 --> 00:30:38,790
are indeed a natural pair.

656
00:30:40,160 --> 00:30:42,310
If they were truly fond of each other,
that would be even better.

657
00:30:42,310 --> 00:30:44,590
Given the Princess's beauty and kindness,

658
00:30:44,590 --> 00:30:46,440
Liu Chu would surely fall into
that softness

659
00:30:46,440 --> 00:30:48,100
and be unable to free himself.

660
00:30:48,440 --> 00:30:49,400
Remember

661
00:30:49,590 --> 00:30:52,110
this is just one part of our many plans.

662
00:30:52,830 --> 00:30:54,550
From now on,

663
00:30:55,350 --> 00:30:57,240
keep a close eye on every step.

664
00:30:57,750 --> 00:30:58,550
I will.

665
00:31:03,310 --> 00:31:04,350
It hurts again?

666
00:31:05,830 --> 00:31:07,720
My heart aches.
